data.title: Westfield Middle School Announces Honor Rolls
meta_keywords: Westfield Middle School Announces Honor Rolls
data.meta_description: WESTFIELD — Middle school merit and honor rolls have been announced by Westfield Academy & Central Schools.   MERIT ROLL: Students earning an average of 85.00
data.text:
WESTFIELD — Middle school merit and honor rolls have been announced by Westfield Academy & Central Schools.

MERIT ROLL: Students earning an average of 85.00-89.499% are awarded recognition by having their names placed on the Merit Roll. The following middle school students make up the Merit Roll for the second marking period of the school year 2023-2024

Sixth Grade: Taylor Burgess, Solomon Freifeld, Kiara LaTorre, Cortland Luke, Dominik Reed.

Seventh Grade: Garrett Black, Kendra Bowen, Nevaeh Dulmus, Owen Ramm, Adalina Rodriguez, Isaiha Zerbey.

Eighth Grade: Madison Cettell, Olivia Kapple, Lucas Kasper, Mason Peters, Robert Schofield, Aiden Simpson, Caleb Stoughton, Braylon Swanson, Reagan Weingart.

HONOR ROLL: Students earning an average of 89.50-94.499% are awarded recognition by having their names placed on the Honor Roll. The following middle school students make up the Honor Roll for the second marking period of the school year 2023-2024

Sixth Grade: Logan Alexander, Alivia Belson, Randy Chimera, Norah Clute, Lillian Crandall, Erik DeGolier, Hazel Estes, Alan Kapple, Katrina Landon, Braxtyn Paddock. Odin Shields, Savannah Stein, Elsa Thomas, Nicholas Thompson.

Seventh Grade: Jacob Baughman, George Chapman, Addison Close, Milyn Cooney, Paige Cornelius, Caleb Freifeld, Ella Maring, Aneyssa Orazio, Iris Pacanowski, Nora Robinson, Liam Simpson.

Eighth Grade: Christopher Bowen, Molly Burgess, Micah Dye, Addison Emery, Adisyn Jaynes, Tyler Jaynes, Raegan Luce, Kadence Phillips, Max Roets, Claire Schofield, Charles Snyder.

HIGH HONOR/ACADEMIC ALL-STAR ROLL: Students earning an average of 94.50-100.00% are awarded recognition by having their names placed on the High Honor/Academic All-Star Roll. The following middle school students make up the High Honor/Academic All-Star Roll for the second marking period of the school year 2023-2024.

Sixth Grade: Bennett Campbell, Brian Conley, Emerson Dodd, Taneka Donovan, Mykel Douglas, Lucas Fuller, Grady Kelley, Greysson Lanphere, Brian Luna-Lopez, Ethan Tunison, Neveya Wells, Liam Zakrajsek.

Eighth Grade: Gracie Bane, Christian Baughman, Alexander Bourgeois, John Bratton, Summer Chimera, Elton Estes, Sara Kelwaski, Ian Kindermann, Isabella Kurtz, Meredith Lendt, Ayden Reese, Joseph Russo, Annabelle Thies, Amelia Zakrajsek.
